      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     opn-fil-kk0-999.
       opn-fil-kk0-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se il pathname per il file [kk0] e' gia' stato  *
      *              * determinato                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       opn-fil-kk0-625.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Open file [kk0] in i-o                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           open      i-o    kk0                                       .
       opn-fil-kk0-650.
