                     w-stp-clc-pdv-v03    >    zero
                     move  zero           to   w-stp-clc-pdv-p01
                     go to stp-clc-pdv-330.
           move      w-stp-clc-pdv-v03    to   w-stp-clc-pdv-p02      .
           subtract  w-stp-clc-pdv-v02    from w-stp-clc-pdv-p02      .
           multiply  100                  by   w-stp-clc-pdv-p02      .
